      "seed": 136759173,
      "version": 7,
      "versionNonce": 1050697509,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1781247251077,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "-> for changing text content - tag inside it consider as plain text\n\nheading1.textContent = \"Hi, this heading text is changed.\";\n\n-> innerHtml - tags inside it will actively structure dom.\n\nconst box = document.getElementById(\"box\");\n\nbox.innerHTML = `<p>Hello my name is Bob. I like to play cricket. i am a professional bowling all-rounder.</p>\n        <button>Click me</button>`;\n\n-> createElement :\n\nconst li = document.createElement(\"li\");\n\n-> append -> add element to dom structure.\n\nlist1.appendChild(li);",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "-> for changing text content - tag inside it consider as plain text\n\nheading1.textContent = \"Hi, this heading text is changed.\";\n\n-> innerHtml - tags inside it will actively structure dom.\n\nconst box = document.getElementById(\"box\");\n\nbox.innerHTML = `<p>Hello my name is Bob. I like to play cricket. i am a professional bowling all-rounder.</p>\n        <button>Click me</button>`;\n\n-> createElement :\n\nconst li = document.createElement(\"li\");\n\n-> append -> add element to dom structure.\n\nlist1.appendChild(li);",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
