      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1781585827019,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "* instead of applying operation over each and every element.\n  if we will apply an operation (adding event listner) on its parent element,\n  that process will be efficient",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "* instead of applying operation over each and every element.\n  if we will apply an operation (adding event listner) on its parent element,\n  that process will be efficient",
